    "description": "<p>About One Focus<br>\nWe are a dynamic and growing Singapore-based SME specialising in Mechanical and Electrical (M&amp;E) services, with a core focus on Addition &amp; Alteration (A&amp;A) works for building projects</p>\n<p><br>\nWhy Join Us?<br>\nAt One Focus, we believe that our people are our greatest asset. We offer a collaborative work environment where your ideas, initiative, and dedication make a real impact. As part of a lean and focused team, you’ll enjoy hands-on exposure to diverse M&amp;E project scopes, career growth opportunities, and the satisfaction of building meaningful and sustainable spaces.<br>\n</p>",
